cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with object pose estimation using RGB-D features, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves learning from data using a neural network, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of uncertainty scores, which is a common topic in graphics (cs.GR).
